Package: Rparadox
Title: R Bindings for the Paradox Database Library
Version: 0.1.6.1.8
Authors@R: 
    person("Daniil", "Popov", , "popov.daniil@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Description: Provides an interface to the 'pxlib' C library for reading data from Paradox database files.
  This package allows users to import data from .db and .mb files into R data structures like tibbles, supporting various Paradox data types.
